title: IBM Lotus Symphony, beta4 for GNU/Linux
description:
This the Lotus Symphony office suite by IBM, BETA4 for GNU/Linux
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^

Be aware, IBM also distributes this software gratis for multiple
platforms on their website:
 <a href="
http://symphony.lotus.com/software/lotus/symphony/home.jspa" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://symphony.lotus.com/software/lotus/symphony/home.jspa</a>

Directions for use:

    use GNU/Linux (this is not for Windows, to check if you are
                   using GNU/Linux or Windows, place your head
                   in a commode and pull the lever repeatedly)

    UnRAR
    execute file
    enjoy


Please remember to leave many silly requests for support in the
comments section of this webpage for me to ridicule or ignore!
